1
00:00:03,437 --> 00:00:07,107
(Zhen Residence)

2
00:00:07,575 --> 00:00:12,620
(20 years ago,
12th year of Chengshun Reign)

3
00:00:14,462 --> 00:00:19,095
(Xiao Congrong,
Defender-General of the State)

4
00:00:21,460 --> 00:00:23,420
Xiao Congrong, hear the decree!

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:26,979
By the Mandate of Heaven,

6
00:00:26,980 --> 00:00:28,900
the Emperor proclaims,

7
00:00:29,060 --> 00:00:31,219
Xiao Congrong
and her husband, Zhen Xiujin,

8
00:00:31,220 --> 00:00:32,900
are charged with treason.

9
00:00:33,260 --> 00:00:36,380
You are hereby ordered to
surrender your military authority

10
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:38,460
and await judgment.

11
00:00:39,420 --> 00:00:40,580
That's impossible.

12
00:00:40,700 --> 00:00:43,020
The Zhen family has always
been loyal to the nation.

13
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:44,979
Someone must be
scheming behind the scenes,

14
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:46,659
sowing discord between
Xiujin and His Majesty.

15
00:00:46,660 --> 00:00:47,819
Do not be hasty.

16
00:00:47,820 --> 00:00:50,539
His Majesty has a second decree.

17
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:51,539
His Majesty said

18
00:00:51,540 --> 00:00:53,779
should General Xiao refuse
to obey the imperial order,

19
00:00:53,780 --> 00:00:55,059
it will be construed as rebellion.

20
00:00:55,059 --> 00:00:57,599
And she, along with the hundred
thousand soldiers of the Xiao Army,

21
00:00:57,599 --> 00:01:00,260
will be executed.

22
00:01:00,620 --> 00:01:01,619
I don't believe this.

23
00:01:01,620 --> 00:01:03,540
I want to see the decree myself.

24
00:01:05,860 --> 00:01:07,179
My words

25
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:09,140
are the decree.

26
00:01:23,287 --> 00:01:28,299
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

27
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:32,899
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

28
00:01:32,900 --> 00:01:34,399
♪By your side once♪

29
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:37,474
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

30
00:01:37,475 --> 00:01:41,449
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

31
00:01:41,450 --> 00:01:46,370
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

32
00:01:46,387 --> 00:01:51,099
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

33
00:01:51,100 --> 00:01:55,661
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

34
00:01:55,662 --> 00:02:00,845
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

35
00:02:01,125 --> 00:02:03,557
=Shall We Dance=

36
00:02:03,575 --> 00:02:06,507
=Episode 2=

37
00:02:07,025 --> 00:02:10,739
(10 years ago,
22nd year of Chengshun Reign)

38
00:02:10,740 --> 00:02:12,019
Xiao Man, you know,

39
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:14,979
His Majesty's accession
today was so scary!

40
00:02:14,980 --> 00:02:17,139
The hall was full of bad people.

41
00:02:17,140 --> 00:02:19,099
But His Majesty was
so tall and majestic,

42
00:02:19,100 --> 00:02:20,339
so handsome and dashing.

43
00:02:20,340 --> 00:02:21,700
He just...

44
00:02:22,380 --> 00:02:23,900
Have you...

45
00:02:23,940 --> 00:02:26,300
Have you been crying?

46
00:02:27,940 --> 00:02:29,499
I'm leaving.

47
00:02:29,500 --> 00:02:32,939
A master has summoned me to serve them.

48
00:02:32,940 --> 00:02:35,539
I don't even know
which palace I'll be sent to.

49
00:02:35,540 --> 00:02:39,220
I won't be able to come here anymore.

50
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:43,740
Then who's going to take care
of Little Flower's and my dinner?

51
00:02:50,900 --> 00:02:52,419
I've saved up

52
00:02:52,420 --> 00:02:55,019
these little pastries over a long time.

53
00:02:55,020 --> 00:02:56,899
They're all for you and Little Flower.

54
00:02:56,900 --> 00:02:58,419
Eat more.

55
00:02:58,420 --> 00:03:00,700
That's a lot.

56
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:06,699
I carved this for a long time.

57
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:08,299
It's for you.

58
00:03:08,300 --> 00:03:11,300
We might not see each other again.

59
00:03:11,460 --> 00:03:13,459
So let it keep you company

60
00:03:13,460 --> 00:03:16,179
when I can't.

61
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:17,299
It really looks like you.

62
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:20,820
And this one will stand in for you,
to keep me company.

63
00:03:23,700 --> 00:03:24,819
Don't worry.

64
00:03:24,820 --> 00:03:27,860
We'll meet again someday.

65
00:03:28,140 --> 00:03:30,540
I don't want to leave you.

66
00:03:40,712 --> 00:03:42,820
(Jia Yi, Chief Eunuch)

67
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:50,259
Are you Xiao Man?

68
00:03:50,260 --> 00:03:51,340
Yes.

69
00:03:51,420 --> 00:03:53,140
Can you dance?

70
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:54,299
Huh?

71
00:03:54,300 --> 00:03:55,499
Huh what?

72
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:56,540
Dance now.

73
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:02,300
Please be careful.

74
00:04:04,740 --> 00:04:07,700
What are you doing here, Big Flower?

75
00:04:07,780 --> 00:04:08,419
Oh,

76
00:04:08,420 --> 00:04:09,419
I know.

77
00:04:09,420 --> 00:04:12,140
We've been assigned to the same master.

78
00:04:13,180 --> 00:04:13,859
No.

79
00:04:13,860 --> 00:04:15,459
I'm your

80
00:04:15,460 --> 00:04:17,700
new master.

81
00:04:17,740 --> 00:04:20,219
So you knew Xiao Man, Your Majesty?

82
00:04:20,220 --> 00:04:22,179
No wonder you
specifically requested him.

83
00:04:22,180 --> 00:04:23,859
You're the Emperor?

84
00:04:23,860 --> 00:04:25,379
I am the Emperor!

85
00:04:25,380 --> 00:04:26,219
Are you surprised?

86
00:04:26,220 --> 00:04:27,660
Didn't see this coming, did you?

87
00:04:32,060 --> 00:04:33,539
Long live

88
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:35,740
Your Majesty.

89
00:04:37,620 --> 00:04:40,500
We're friends.
You don't have to do that.

90
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:42,379
How could someone like me

91
00:04:42,380 --> 00:04:44,939
ever be friends with Your Majesty?

92
00:04:44,940 --> 00:04:47,059
I want to be friends with you.

93
00:04:47,060 --> 00:04:48,619
If you don't agree,

94
00:04:48,620 --> 00:04:50,179
I'll...

95
00:04:50,180 --> 00:04:51,300
I'll...

96
00:04:52,940 --> 00:04:53,779
Careful, Your Majesty!

97
00:04:53,780 --> 00:04:56,140
I'm not getting up until you agree.

98
00:05:06,460 --> 00:05:08,299
I should've told you earlier.

99
00:05:08,300 --> 00:05:09,419
I'm sorry

100
00:05:09,420 --> 00:05:10,579
that I scared you.

101
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:11,659
I won't do that again.

102
00:05:11,660 --> 00:05:14,219
Didn't you say the Emperor
was tall and imposing,

103
00:05:14,220 --> 00:05:15,979
handsome and dashing?

104
00:05:15,980 --> 00:05:18,179
Xiao Man, we'll grow up together.

105
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:20,499
One day, I'll be tall and imposing,

106
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:21,699
handsome and commanding.

107
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:23,180
Are you happy now?

108
00:05:33,862 --> 00:05:35,419
(Six Months Later,
1st year of Hongzheng Reign)

109
00:05:35,420 --> 00:05:36,179
Big Flower,

110
00:05:36,180 --> 00:05:37,059
I'm scared.

111
00:05:37,060 --> 00:05:38,179
Leave the kite.

112
00:05:38,180 --> 00:05:39,779
I'll make you another one.

113
00:05:39,780 --> 00:05:40,899
No way.

114
00:05:40,900 --> 00:05:44,260
We made that kite together.

115
00:05:44,620 --> 00:05:45,740
Big Flower!

116
00:05:49,380 --> 00:05:50,099
Big Flower!

117
00:05:50,100 --> 00:05:50,779
Big Flower!

118
00:05:50,780 --> 00:05:51,900
Big Flower!

119
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:55,420
These useless servants
failed to protect their master.

120
00:05:55,860 --> 00:05:57,219
Flog them all to death.

121
00:05:57,220 --> 00:05:58,340
Yes, Your Highness.

122
00:05:58,780 --> 00:05:59,819
Your Highness,

123
00:05:59,820 --> 00:06:00,979
please spare the child's life.

124
00:06:00,980 --> 00:06:02,660
Just banish him from the palace.

125
00:06:04,340 --> 00:06:06,540
Disobedient servants

126
00:06:06,580 --> 00:06:08,620
should be taught a lesson.

127
00:06:08,980 --> 00:06:10,300
Mercy, Your Highness!

128
00:06:11,980 --> 00:06:12,939
Your Highness,

129
00:06:12,940 --> 00:06:14,299
he's still young.

130
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:17,700
Please show mercy, Your Highness!

131
00:06:21,980 --> 00:06:23,460
Stop...

132
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:29,339
Aunt,

133
00:06:29,340 --> 00:06:30,779
I'm begging you,

134
00:06:30,780 --> 00:06:32,779
please tell them to stop.

135
00:06:32,780 --> 00:06:34,140
Aunt...

136
00:06:35,780 --> 00:06:37,300
You care about him?

137
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:40,220
Stop.

138
00:06:40,580 --> 00:06:41,619
Issue my order,

139
00:06:41,620 --> 00:06:43,299
banish this wretched slave
from the palace.

140
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:44,300
Yes, Your Highness.

141
00:06:45,860 --> 00:06:46,980
Chu Ying,

142
00:06:47,580 --> 00:06:48,980
remember this,

143
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:51,060
the one who sits on the throne

144
00:06:51,140 --> 00:06:53,300
cannot afford to have a weakness.

145
00:07:02,260 --> 00:07:03,580
Xiao Man!

146
00:07:11,940 --> 00:07:12,899
Big Flower,

147
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:14,980
I'm leaving.

148
00:07:31,850 --> 00:07:35,595
♪I wanted to ask you
the meaning of forever♪

149
00:07:36,050 --> 00:07:39,270
♪Is it longing that never rests♪

150
00:07:39,875 --> 00:07:42,845
♪Love that echoes without end♪

151
00:07:44,412 --> 00:07:47,870
♪Or promises that can't be kept♪

152
00:07:48,260 --> 00:07:48,979
Xiao Man,

153
00:07:48,980 --> 00:07:50,500
listen to me.

154
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:53,379
Whether it takes three years,
five years, or many more,

155
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:55,619
I will be here,

156
00:07:55,620 --> 00:07:57,299
in this vast imperial palace,

157
00:07:57,300 --> 00:07:59,036
waiting for you to return.

158
00:07:59,037 --> 00:08:02,049
♪How cruel♪

159
00:08:02,050 --> 00:08:06,682
♪Love blooms and withers♪

160
00:08:08,425 --> 00:08:12,049
♪The more I try to forget
the fiercer the love burns♪

161
00:08:12,050 --> 00:08:13,900
(10 years later)

162
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:16,819
(Chu Ying)

163
00:08:17,387 --> 00:08:20,649
♪How am I supposed to let go♪

164
00:08:20,650 --> 00:08:22,019
♪And bring this story to an end♪

165
00:08:22,020 --> 00:08:23,340
Your Majesty,

166
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:25,899
it's time to attend court.

167
00:08:25,900 --> 00:08:28,180
The affairs of state must come first.

168
00:08:32,940 --> 00:08:34,060
Very well.

169
00:08:34,540 --> 00:08:35,411
Let's go to court.

170
00:08:35,412 --> 00:08:42,332
♪How absurd that this longing
just won't die♪

171
00:08:42,900 --> 00:08:44,539
I have a petition.

172
00:08:44,540 --> 00:08:46,499
His Majesty has now reached adulthood.

173
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:47,579
According to ancestral law,

174
00:08:47,580 --> 00:08:49,619
the Grand Princess
should return authority

175
00:08:49,620 --> 00:08:53,019
and the Tiger Tally of
the military to His Majesty.

176
00:08:53,020 --> 00:08:55,419
With the border regions unstable

177
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:57,739
and the tribes growing restless,

178
00:08:57,740 --> 00:09:00,939
I stationed the army
to protect His Majesty.

179
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:02,660
What's wrong with that?

180
00:09:04,180 --> 00:09:06,280
His Majesty has only just taken
personal control of governance.

181
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,819
He hasn't rushed this,

182
00:09:07,820 --> 00:09:09,860
Director Jia hasn't rushed this,

183
00:09:10,260 --> 00:09:11,540
yet you, Minister He,

184
00:09:11,700 --> 00:09:13,459
you seem awfully eager.

185
00:09:13,460 --> 00:09:14,619
Your Highness,

186
00:09:14,620 --> 00:09:16,499
you are but a woman,

187
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:19,780
yet who has held the reins of court for years,
this already runs contrary to propriety.

188
00:09:20,260 --> 00:09:21,099
Now that

189
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:23,299
His Majesty has assumed personal rule,

190
00:09:23,300 --> 00:09:24,179
I advise you

191
00:09:24,180 --> 00:09:26,099
not to defy

192
00:09:26,100 --> 00:09:28,580
the ancestral precepts.

193
00:09:30,180 --> 00:09:31,179
Minister He,

194
00:09:31,180 --> 00:09:32,539
loyalty to the throne

195
00:09:32,540 --> 00:09:34,299
knows no distinction
between man and woman.

196
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:36,899
Such a view is rather
narrow-minded, is it not?

197
00:09:36,900 --> 00:09:39,580
And it's equally improper for a prince consort
to meddle in state affairs.

198
00:09:39,900 --> 00:09:40,899
You two have been

199
00:09:40,900 --> 00:09:42,139
backing each other at court

200
00:09:42,140 --> 00:09:43,619
these days.

201
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:44,820
Doesn't that

202
00:09:45,060 --> 00:09:46,819
raise questions about your intentions?

203
00:09:46,820 --> 00:09:48,579
How impressive, Minister He.

204
00:09:48,580 --> 00:09:50,659
So quick to make baseless accusations.

205
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:52,660
That is hardly the conduct
of a gentleman.

206
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:54,420
Your Majesty, please judge clearly.

207
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:56,120
Since entering public service,

208
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:58,120
my principle has always been
to side with reason, not kinship.

209
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:59,339
And in this matter,

210
00:09:59,340 --> 00:10:02,180
reason undeniably
lies with Her Highness.

211
00:10:07,020 --> 00:10:08,099
A well-reasoned argument.

212
00:10:08,100 --> 00:10:09,420
Well-reasoned indeed.

213
00:10:10,060 --> 00:10:11,139
Your Majesty,

214
00:10:11,140 --> 00:10:12,860
in my humble opinion,

215
00:10:12,940 --> 00:10:16,040
Her Highness should indeed
return command of the army.

216
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:18,059
She may then continue to
govern from behind the screen,

217
00:10:18,060 --> 00:10:19,339
guiding you, Your Majesty.

218
00:10:19,340 --> 00:10:20,059
Wouldn't that

219
00:10:20,060 --> 00:10:22,140
satisfy all parties?

220
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:26,800
The Directorate of Ceremonial has
held sway over court affairs for years,

221
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:28,779
with eyes and ears everywhere.

222
00:10:28,780 --> 00:10:31,859
If I were to hand the command
of the army over to you now,

223
00:10:31,860 --> 00:10:34,020
one wonders, would those soldiers

224
00:10:34,060 --> 00:10:35,900
pledge loyalty to the name Chu,

225
00:10:36,220 --> 00:10:38,220
or to the name Jia?

226
00:10:40,940 --> 00:10:42,300
Director Jia,

227
00:10:42,660 --> 00:10:44,099
tell me,

228
00:10:44,100 --> 00:10:45,340
am I right?

229
00:10:46,020 --> 00:10:47,659
I would never dare.

230
00:10:47,660 --> 00:10:48,339
I only

231
00:10:48,340 --> 00:10:51,100
wish to spare His Majesty
from petty burdens.

232
00:10:51,540 --> 00:10:53,979
Your Highness, if you act
in this manner,

233
00:10:53,980 --> 00:10:56,420
I fear the entire court

234
00:10:56,540 --> 00:10:58,860
will call you a tyrant.

235
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:05,340
Since you think I'm a tyrant,

236
00:11:05,900 --> 00:11:08,820
then a tyrant I shall be today.

237
00:11:14,620 --> 00:11:16,660
And as a tyrant,

238
00:11:16,700 --> 00:11:20,180
I am even more convinced now is
not the ideal time to return power.

239
00:11:25,220 --> 00:11:27,420
How wonderful!

240
00:11:27,620 --> 00:11:29,500
With Aunt to my left,

241
00:11:29,740 --> 00:11:31,379
Director Jia to my right,

242
00:11:31,380 --> 00:11:33,660
and Minister He protecting me
from the front,

243
00:11:33,780 --> 00:11:36,500
it's like being nestled within
a ring of protective mountains.

244
00:11:36,740 --> 00:11:37,739
I do so adore this feeling

245
00:11:37,740 --> 00:11:39,580
of being utterly sheltered.

246
00:11:49,660 --> 00:11:51,019
His Majesty is an adult now.

247
00:11:51,020 --> 00:11:52,539
Yet he's dancing in the court.

248
00:11:52,540 --> 00:11:53,619
This is utterly improper.

249
00:11:53,620 --> 00:11:54,299
What are

250
00:11:54,300 --> 00:11:55,019
we to do?

251
00:11:55,020 --> 00:11:57,179
Such childish behavior.

252
00:11:57,180 --> 00:11:58,620
I'm afraid our nation is...

253
00:11:59,060 --> 00:12:01,139
Mind your tongue!

254
00:12:01,140 --> 00:12:04,300
Are we just going to say
nothing to His Majesty?

255
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:07,579
Xiao Man,

256
00:12:07,580 --> 00:12:09,099
it's time you return to the palace.

257
00:12:09,100 --> 00:12:09,819
Yes,

258
00:12:09,820 --> 00:12:10,900
Godfather.

259
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:20,370
(Xiao Man)

260
00:12:30,775 --> 00:12:34,695
♪I wanted to ask you
the meaning of forever♪

261
00:12:35,100 --> 00:12:38,220
♪Is it longing that never rests♪

262
00:12:38,875 --> 00:12:42,132
♪Love that echoes without end♪

263
00:12:43,425 --> 00:12:47,020
♪Or promises that can't be kept♪

264
00:12:48,975 --> 00:12:52,395
♪All those vows of forever we made♪

265
00:12:52,937 --> 00:12:56,382
♪Are sealed away in darkness now♪

266
00:12:58,175 --> 00:13:00,982
♪How cruel♪

267
00:13:01,100 --> 00:13:05,257
♪Love blooms and withers♪

268
00:13:07,450 --> 00:13:11,532
♪The more I try to forget
the fiercer the love burns♪

269
00:13:11,825 --> 00:13:15,920
♪The more I retreat
the sharper it feels♪

270
00:13:16,287 --> 00:13:19,599
♪How am I supposed to let go♪

271
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:23,682
♪And bring this story to an end♪
